3. conditional logic can be removed

if (row < 1 || row > rowcolBound || col < 1 || col > rowcolBound) {
            return false;
        }
        else {
            return true;
        }

改为
return !(row < 1 || row > rowcolBound || col < 1 || col > rowcolBound);
